---
/**
 * ValueSection — Provisional "why cost visibility matters" section.
 * id="value" required by 03-page-structure.md for anchor linking.
 * Content is provisional and should be reviewed by stakeholders.
 * Spec: 03-page-structure.md (section anchor)
 */
---

<section id="value" class="value-section" style="scroll-margin-top: var(--nav-height)">
  <div class="container value-inner">
    <div class="value-header">
      <p class="eyebrow">The Problem</p>
      <h2 class="value-heading">Why cost visibility matters at the source</h2>
      <p class="value-subtext">
        Discovering cost overruns after deployment means expensive rework, delayed releases, and uncomfortable conversations with finance. The earlier you catch cost issues, the cheaper they are to fix.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="value-grid">
      <div class="value-card card">
        <div class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <!-- Heroicons: exclamation-triangle (MIT) -->
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 9v3.75m-9.303 3.376c-.866 1.5.217 3.374 1.948 3.374h14.71c1.73 0 2.813-1.874 1.948-3.374L13.949 3.378c-.866-1.5-3.032-1.5-3.898 0L2.697 16.126ZM12 15.75h.007v.008H12v-.008Z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="card-title">Caught late, cost more</h3>
        <p class="card-body">A misconfigured instance spotted at code review costs minutes to fix. The same issue found in production costs days of incident response and thousands in unexpected spend.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="value-card card">
        <div class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <!-- Heroicons: tag (MIT) -->
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M9.568 3H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 3 5.25v4.318c0 .597.237 1.17.659 1.591l9.581 9.581c.699.699 1.78.872 2.607.33a18.095 18.095 0 0 0 5.223-5.223c.542-.827.369-1.908-.33-2.607L11.16 3.66A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 9.568 3Z" />
            <path d="M6 6h.008v.008H6V6Z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="card-title">Tagging debt compounds</h3>
        <p class="card-body">Untagged resources are invisible to FinOps teams. Every untagged resource deployed today becomes a compliance gap, a cost attribution blind spot, and a manual cleanup task next quarter.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="value-card card">
        <div class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <!-- Heroicons: check-badge (MIT) -->
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12c0 1.268-.63 2.39-1.593 3.068a3.745 3.745 0 0 1-1.043 3.296 3.745 3.745 0 0 1-3.296 1.043A3.745 3.745 0 0 1 12 21c-1.268 0-2.39-.63-3.068-1.593a3.745 3.745 0 0 1-3.296-1.043 3.745 3.745 0 0 1-1.043-3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0 1 3 12c0-1.268.63-2.39 1.593-3.068a3.745 3.745 0 0 1 1.043-3.296 3.745 3.745 0 0 1 3.296-1.043A3.745 3.745 0 0 1 12 3c1.268 0 2.39.63 3.068 1.593a3.745 3.745 0 0 1 3.296 1.043 3.745 3.745 0 0 1 1.043 3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0 1 21 12Z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="card-title">Compliance from the&nbsp;start</h3>
        <p class="card-body">When cost and compliance awareness is built into your IaC authoring workflow, engineers ship compliant infrastructure on the first try — eliminating the FinOps review bottleneck entirely.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .value-section {
    padding: var(--space-24) 0;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .value-inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-16);
  }

  .value-header {
    max-width: 56ch;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .value-heading {
    font-size: clamp(var(--text-3xl), 4vw, var(--text-4xl));
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .value-subtext {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .value-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .value-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .value-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .value-card {
    padding: var(--space-8);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .card-icon {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    color: var(--color-accent-primary);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .card-icon svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .card-title {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .card-body {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }
</style>
